\c 26 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 26\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Guutummaatti Of Kennuu (Kan Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* Ani balleessaa tokko malee deddeebi'eera, amanannaa hin raafamnes Waaqayyo irra kaa'adheera, yaa Waaqayyo, ati dhugaa koo anaaf baasi.
\m \bd 2\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, qorii na ilaali, yaada koo fi garaa koo ati fonqolchi!
\m \bd 3\bd* Gaarummaan kee ija koo dura jira, siif amanamuudhaanis nan deddeebi'e.
\m \bd 4\bd* Ani namoota sobduu wajjin tarree hin teenye, warra haxxee wajjinis hidhata hin taane.
\m \bd 5\bd* Ani walga'ii warra hamaa godhanii nan jibbe, warra jal'ootaa wajjinis hin teenye.
\m \bd 6\bd* Yakka sababiin hin qabneef, harka koo nan dhiqadha, iddoo aarsaa kee nan naanna'a, yaa Waaqayyo!
\m \bd 7\bd* Faarfannaa galataa guddisee faarfachaa, gochaa kee isa dinqisiisaa hundumaa nan hima.
\m \bd 8\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, mana ati keessa jiraattu, iddoo ulfinni kee buufatus ani nan jaalladha. 
\m \bd 9\bd* Lubbuu koo kan warra cubbamootaa wajjin hin fuudhin, warra dhiiga namaa dhangalaasanii wajjinis jireenya koo hin balleessin.
\m \bd 10\bd* Harka warra akkasii keessa akeeki hamaa hojjechuu jira, harka isaanii mirgaa keessa immoo gabbarsuutu guute.
\m \bd 11\bd* Ani garuu balleessaa malee nan deddeebi'a, yaa Waaqayyo, ati na furi, anatti araaramis.
\m \bd 12\bd* Miilli koo lafa wal qixxee irra qajeelee in dhaabata, walga'ii keessattis Waaqayyoon nan jajadha!
\b 
